app-example

# generated native folders (Option B: /ios curated tracking; /android still ignored
# except for the placeholder README that documents the hybrid pattern — see
# apps/studio/mobile/android/README.md and apps/studio/mobile/ios/README.md).
# Phase 8H-2 widened the rule from `/android` to `/android/**` so the
# `!/android/README.md` exception below can take effect (gitignore can re-include
# a file only when its parent directory is not itself excluded).
/android/**
!/android/README.md

# Local-only superseded icon backups (kept on disk, not tracked)
/assets/images/icon.iphone-before-attitude-indicator.png
/assets/images/icon.original.png
